<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<style type="text/css" media="screen">
	:root {
		 /* Site Elements */
		/* background select input */
		--color-site-1: #F5F4F2;
		--color-site-1-c:   #000000; /* foreground */
		--color-site-1-c-1: hsl(0, 0%, 42%); /* secondary foreground */
		--color-accent-1-1: #007ea8;
		--color-site-1-2:   #D9D9D9; /* details - border line */
		--color-accent-1: #00688C;
		--color-accent-1-c:   #FFFFFF; /* foreground */
		    /* Site Elements */
		--color-site-2:     #FFFFFF; /* background */
		--color-site-2-c:   #222222; /* foreground */
		--color-site-2-1:   #e2e8f0; /* details - border line */
		/* Oracle red */
		--color-site-3: #c74934; /* Color taken from figma spec wireframe */

	}

	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	html {
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
	}

	html, body {
		height: 100%
	}

	body {
		background-color: var( --color-site-1 ) !important;
		margin: 0;
		background-repeat: repeat;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		background: url("data:image/png;base64,");
	}

	body {
    scrollbar-color: #d3d3d3 #efefef;
    scrollbar-width: 12px;
	}

	::-webkit-scrollbar {
		width:12px;
		height:12px;
		background-color: #efefef;
	}

	::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
		background-color:#d3d3d3;
		border-radius: 0.25rem;
		border: 1px solid #efefef;
	}

	::-webkit-scrollbar-corner {
		background: #efefef;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__body::-webkit-scrollbar {
		background-color: #333333;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
		background-color:#999999;
		border-color: #333;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__body::-webkit-scrollbar-corner {
		background: #333333;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__body {
		scrollbar-color: #999999 #333333;
	}

	.ords-logo {
		background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;base64,");
		display: block;
		width: 6rem;
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		margin: auto;
		transform: translateY(50%);
	}


	main {
		text-align: center;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
	}

	main .main-box h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: normal;
		margin: 2.5rem auto auto auto;
	}

	main .main-box h3 {
		font-weight: normal;
		margin: 1rem 0 1rem 0;
	}

	main .main-box h3 span {
		color: var(--color-site-3);
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	main .main-box p {
		color: var(--color-site-1-c-1);
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;

	}

	main .main-box p span {
		color: var(--color-site-1-c);
	}

	main .main-box .reasons {
		margin: auto;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
	}

	main .main-box .reasons p {
		color: var(--color-site-1-c-1);
		margin: 2.25rem auto 2.25rem auto;
		color: black;
		text-align: left;
		width: auto;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	main .main-box {
		margin: 0 auto;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 20px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 10%);
		background-color: var(--color-site-2);
		border-color: var(--color-site-2-1);
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 0.2rem;
		transition: all 0.5s;
		min-width: calc(320px - 2rem);
		width: 45rem;
	}

	main .main-box.expanded {
		width: 80rem;
		transition: all 0.6s;
	}

	main .main-box .sign-in-button {
		border: none;
		width: fit-content;
		min-width: 8rem;
		height: 2.5rem;
		background-color: var(--color-accent-1);
		border-radius: 0.3rem;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		cursor: pointer;
		text-decoration: none;
    	color: var(--color-accent-1-c);
	}

	main .main-box .sign-in-button:hover {
		background-color: var(--color-accent-1-1);
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	.container {
		flex-grow: 1;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.layout {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		box-sizing: border-box;
		letter-spacing: 0.176px;
	}

	.collapsible {
		width: auto;
		background-color: var(--color-site-3);
		border-radius: 0.3rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		margin: 1rem 0;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__header {
		flex: 1;
		width: auto;
		border-radius: 0.3rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0.75rem;
		padding-left: 0;
		justify-content: space-between;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__header .copy-button {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__header .header-buttons-right {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__header a {
		margin: 0 0.5rem;
		display: flex;
		cursor: pointer;
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__header .collapsed .open {
		display: block
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__header svg {
		width: 1.5rem;
		fill: var(--color-site-1);
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		margin: auto;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__header svg.clone {
		margin: auto;
		fill: var(--color-site-1-c);
		width: auto !important;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__header .collapsed .chevron-right{
		display: none !important;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__header .chevron-down{
		display: none;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__header .collapsed .chevron-down{
		display: block !important;
		margin-left: 0.2rem;
    	margin-top: 0.2rem;
	}
	
	.collapsible .collapsible__header h3 {
		color: var(--color-site-1);
		margin: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex:1;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__body {
		background-color: var(--color-site-2-c);
		position: relative;
		border-radius: 0 0 0.3rem 0.3rem;
		padding: 0;
		display: flex;
		max-height: 40rem;
		overflow: auto;
		text-align: justify;
		transition: all 0.6s;
		height: 0;
		overflow: hidden !important;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__body.collapsed {
		overflow: auto !important;
		height: 40rem;
		transition: all 0.5s;
		padding: 1rem;
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__body code {
		color: var(--color-site-1-2) !important;
		position: absolute;
		text-align: left;
		font-family: 'Hack','monospace', 'monospace';
	}

	.collapsible .collapsible__body pre {
		margin: 0.5rem;
	}


	footer {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		align-items: center;
		padding-left: 1rem;
		font-size: .80rem;
		color: var(--color-site-1-c-1);
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.external-links-container {
		padding: 0;
		flex-grow: 0;
		margin: auto;
	}

	.external-links {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.external-links li {
		list-style: none;
		border-right: 1px solid var(--color-site-1-2);
		margin: auto;
		padding-right: 1rem;
	}

	.external-links li:first-child {
		padding-left: 0;
	}

	.external-links li:last-child {
		border-right: none;
	}

	.external-links a, .external-links a:visited {
		text-decoration: none;
		color: inherit;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.external-links a:hover, .external-links a:focus {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.copyright {
		flex-grow: 1;
		text-align: right;
		margin: 0 1rem;
		white-space: nowrap;
		color: var(--color-site-1-c);
		max-height: 40px;
    	margin: auto 1rem auto;
	}

	.oracle-logo {
		text-align: right;
		padding: 0;
		position: relative;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		margin-right: 1rem;
	}

	.oracle-logo figure {
		width: 2.5rem;
		display: block;
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		background-size: contain;
		margin: auto 0;
		background-image: url( 'data:image/png;base64,' );
	}

	.oracle {
		display: flex;
		margin: auto;
		flex-grow: 1;
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		main .main-box {
			max-width: 90vw !important;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 1200px) {
		.external-links li {
			margin: auto;
			padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
		}
		.oracle {
			flex-grow: 0;
			display: flex;
			margin: auto;
			flex-direction: column;
			width: 100vw;
		}
		.copyright {
			margin: auto;
			padding-top: 1rem;
		}
		.oracle-logo {
			margin: auto;
			padding-top: 2rem;
		}
	}

	@font-face {
    font-family: 'Hack';
    src: url("data:font/ttf;base64,");
}

</style>

<body>

	<div class="container">
		<div class="layout">
			<main>
				<figure class="ords-logo"></figure>
				<section class="main-box" id="mainBox">
					<h1>Unauthorized</h1>
					<h3>HTTP Status Code: <span>401</span></h3>
					<p>Request ID: <span>LyYVmbamFdK6TP-4kCuIhQ</span></p>
					<p>Request Timestamp: <span>2025-11-16T05:37:36.052985Z</span></p>
					<p id="productErrorCode">Error Code: <span></span></p>
					<div id="reasons" class="reasons">
						
						<p>Access to this resource is protected. Please sign in to access this resource.</p>
<a class="sign-in-button" href="http://appit.ignitetechno.com:8080/ords/xapi/sign-in/?r=auth%2Ftoken">Sign in</a>


					</div>
					<div></div>
				</section>
			</main>
		</div>
	</div>
	<footer>
		<div class="external-links-container">
			<ul class="external-links">
				<li>
					<a
						aria-label="About Oracle"
						id="aboutOracle"
						href="https://www.oracle.com/us/corporate/index.html#menu-about"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noreferrer"
					>
						About Oracle
					</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a
						aria-label="Terms Of Use"
						id="termsOfUse"
						href="https://www.oracle.com/us/legal/terms/index.html"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noreferrer"
					>
						Terms Of Use
					</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a
						aria-label="Contact Us"
						id="contactUs"
						href="https://www.oracle.com/us/corporate/contact/index.html"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noreferrer"
					>
						Contact Us
					</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a
						aria-label="Legal Notices"
						id="legalNotices"
						href="https://www.oracle.com/us/legal/index.html"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noreferrer"
					>
						Legal Notices
					</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a
						aria-label="Your Privacy Rights"
						id="yourPrivacyRights"
						href="https://www.oracle.com/us/legal/privacy/index.html"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noreferrer"
					>
						Your Privacy Rights
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="oracle">
			<div class="copyright" aria-label="Oracle Copyright">Copyright  2009, 2023 Oracle and/or its affiliates</div>
			<div class="oracle-logo">
				<a href="https://www.oracle.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
					<figure alt="Oracle logo" alt="Oracle logo"></figure>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>

    <script>
		//Functions to identify current browser using userAgent
		function isSafari() {
			let ret = !!navigator.userAgent.match( /safari/i ) && !navigator.userAgent.match( /chrome/i );
			return ret;
		};

		function isFirefox() {
			let ret = !!navigator.userAgent.match( /firefox/i );
			return ret;
		}

		function isChrome() {
			let ret = !!navigator.userAgent.match( /chrome/i ) && !navigator.userAgent.match( /edge/i );
			return ret;
		};

		function isEdge() {
			let ret = !!navigator.userAgent.match( /edge/i );
			return ret;
		};

		function isIE() {
			let ret = !!navigator.userAgent.match(/trident\//i ) || !!navigator.userAgent.match(/msie /i );
			return ret;
		}

		const mainBox = document.getElementById( 'mainBox' );
		const debugButton = document.getElementById( 'debugButton' );
		const stackButton = document.getElementById( 'stackButton' );
		const downloadButton = document.getElementById( 'downloadButton' );
		const debugBody = document.getElementById( 'debugBody' );
		const stackBody = document.getElementById( 'stackBody' );

		const toogleCollapsibleHeader = ( event ) => {
			const toogleButton = event.currentTarget.querySelector( 'a' );;
			toogleButton.click();
		}

		const toggleCollapsible = ( event ) => {
			event.stopPropagation();
			const collapseButton = event.currentTarget;
			if ( collapseButton.classList.value ){
				collapseButton.classList.remove( 'collapsed' );
				mainBox.classList.remove( 'expanded' );
				if ( collapseButton === debugButton ){
					debugBody.classList.remove( 'collapsed' );
					mainBox.classList.remove( 'expanded' );
				} else {
					stackBody.classList.remove( 'collapsed' ); 
					mainBox.classList.remove( 'expanded' );
				}
			} else {
				collapseButton.classList.add( 'collapsed' );
				mainBox.classList.add( 'expanded' );
				if ( collapseButton === debugButton ){
					debugBody.classList.add( 'collapsed' );
					stackBody.classList.remove( 'collapsed' );
				} else {
					stackBody.classList.add( 'collapsed' ); 
					debugBody.classList.remove( 'collapsed' );
					debugButton.classList.remove( 'collapsed' );
				}
			}

		}

		function download( fileName, text ) {
			let element = document.createElement( 'a' );
			element.setAttribute( 'href', 'data:text/plain;charset=utf-8,' + encodeURIComponent( text ) );
			element.setAttribute( 'download', fileName );
			element.style.display = 'none';
			document.body.appendChild( element );
			element.click();
			document.body.removeChild( element );
		}

		const downloadFile = ( event ) => {
			event.stopPropagation();
			const button = event.currentTarget;
			const selector = button.dataset.clipboardTarget;
			const downloadTarget = document.querySelector( selector );
			const fileName = selector.includes('stack') ? 'stackTrace.log': 'debugTrace.log';
			const downloadText = downloadTarget.textContent || '';
			if( downloadText !== '' ) {
				download( fileName, downloadText );
			}
		}

		function removeEmptyElements() {
			const productErrorCode = document.getElementById( 'productErrorCode' );
			if ( !productErrorCode.lastChild.innerText ) {
				productErrorCode.remove();
			} 
		}

    	removeEmptyElements();

		//Only run this part if stack trace/ debug trace is enabled
		if( debugButton && stackButton ) {
			const collapsibles = document.getElementsByClassName( 'collapsible' );
			const collapsibleHeaers = document.getElementsByClassName( 'collapsible__header' );

			for( let i = 0; i < collapsibles.length; i++ ) {
				let paragraphElement = collapsibles[i].querySelector( 'code' );
				if( !paragraphElement || paragraphElement.innerText == '' ) {
					collapsibles[i].style.display = 'none';
				}
			};

			for( let i = 0; i < collapsibleHeaers.length; i++ ) {
				collapsibleHeaers[i].addEventListener( 'click', toogleCollapsibleHeader );
			};

			debugButton.addEventListener( 'click', toggleCollapsible );
	   		stackButton.addEventListener( 'click', toggleCollapsible );
			downloadButton.addEventListener( 'click', downloadFile );
			let copyButtons = document.querySelectorAll( '.copy-button' );

			copyButtons.forEach( async ( button ) => {
				const copyTarget = document.querySelector( button.dataset.clipboardTarget );
				const copyValue = copyTarget.textContent || '';
				button.addEventListener( 'click', function( event ) {
					event.stopPropagation();
					const textArea = document.createElement( 'textarea' );
					if ( window.isSecureContext ) {
						if ( isFirefox() ||
							isSafari() &&
								navigator.clipboard &&
								typeof navigator.clipboard.writeText === 'function' ) {
								navigator.clipboard.writeText( copyValue );
						} else if ( !isIE() && // not FireFox nor IE
							navigator.clipboard &&
							typeof navigator.clipboard.writeText === 'function' ) {
							navigator.permissions.query( { 'name': 'clipboard-write' } ).then( function( result ) {
								if ( result.state === 'prompt' || result.state === 'granted' ) {
									navigator.clipboard.writeText( copyValue );
								} else {
									throw new Error( result.state );
								}
							} );
						}
					} else {
						const valueLength = copyValue ? copyValue.length - 1 : 0;
						let success;
						const copy = () => {
							const focusEle = document.body;
							try {
								textArea.value = copyValue;
								textArea.focus();
								if ( isIE() ) {
									if ( 'selectionStart' in textArea ) {
										textArea.selectionStart = 0;
										textArea.selectionEnd = valueLength;
										textArea.focus();
									}
								} else {
									textArea.select();
									focusEle && focusEle.focus();
								}
								document.execCommand( 'copy' );
							} finally {
								textArea.value = '';
							}
						};
						if ( isIE() ) {
							copy();
						} else {
							button.onclick = copy;
						}
					}
				})
			} );
		}
		else {
			mainBox.style.transition = 'none';
			mainBox.style.padding = '1.25rem 1.25rem 2rem';
		}
    </script>
</body>

</html>
